<header class="header">
  <h1>Best Repair Kit for Mini Greenhouse Covers</h1>
  <p class="tagline">
    Mini greenhouse covers fail at seams, zippers, and stress points — and the right repair kit keeps them usable much longer.
  </p>
  <p class="lede">
    <strong>For most gardeners, the best repair kit combines UV-resistant patch tape, reinforcement material, and basic tools to handle small tears before they spread.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Mini greenhouse covers are thinner and more flexible than full greenhouse plastic, which makes them more prone to wear. Small damage can quickly turn into large tears if not addressed early.
  </p>
  <p>
    A simple repair kit lets you fix problems quickly and extend the life of your setup.
  </p>
</header>

